Enhancing Personalization User Mappings for Identity Resolution

To successfully use your Marketing Cloud Personalization data in segmentation and activations, map the user fields for Identity Resolution.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience


Products:

Data Cloud
Marketing Cloud Personalization

The users data stream is mapped to Contact Point Email and Party Identification Customer 360 Data Model objects in the data model. With these mappings, you can match Marketing Cloud Personalization user profiles using email or party identification match rules.

DATA SOURCE OBJECT (DSO)	CUSTOMER 360 DATA MODEL OBJECTS
Users DSO	Individual, EmailContactPoint, PartyIdentification
Catalog Events DSO	ProductBrowseEngagement
Cart Events DSO	
Cart Line Events Items DSO	ShoppingCartEngagement
Order Events DSO	ProductOrderEngagement
Order Line Items DSO
